HOT, a Higher-Order Termination prover
See the COPYRIGHTS and LICENSE files.

The compilation procedure that is provided requires a UNIX-like
operating system (Linux or Cygwin) with the following tools:

- GNU bash version 4.1.5 http://www.gnu.org/software/bash/
- GNU sed version 4.2.1 http://www.gnu.org/software/sed/
- GNU make version 3.81 http://www.gnu.org/software/make/
- OCaml version 3.12.1 http://caml.inria.fr/
- Rainbow http://color.inria.fr/

Compilation procedure:

1) cd $rainbow_dir && make lib

2) cd $hot_dir && ./configure $rainbow_dir

3) cd $hot_dir && make depend && make
